(4) Supportive: bisphosphonate (zoledronate monthly) or denosumab (esp CKD) for skeletal events; surgery/RT/vertebroplasty for impending fracture/cord compression; manage hypercalcemia; hydration + careful loop diuretic;

(5) Renal: optimize hydration, avoid nephrotoxin (NSAID, contrast), treat cast nephropathy with rapid disease control; possibly plasmapheresis if AKI + light chain;

