(7) Thromboprophylaxis with lenalidomide (aspirin or apixaban);

(8) Anemia management (EPO, transfusion);

(9) Vaccinations (PCV20, flu, COVID, RSV);

(10) Refractory/relapsed: CAR-T (cilta-cel, ide-cel), bispecific (teclistamab — BCMA, talquetamab — GPRC5D, elranatamab);

(11) Monitor: M-protein, FLC, β2M, monthly initially; long-term survivorship
