(8) Pediatric / pregnancy: critical for fetal neural tube; folate supplement before/during. A ผิด — folate alone harmful. C ผิด — wrong type anemia. D ผิด — overinvasive. E ผิด — schedule wrong.

ตัวเลือก B (รายละเอียด): Acute pyelonephritis in pregnancy with sepsis — Admission + IV antibiotics + supportive:

