(6) Dialysis prep (eGFR < 30 — KDOQI; eGFR 15-20 + symptoms): - Vascular access: AVF creation ≥ 6 mo before anticipated HD start (KDIGO 2019). - Modality discussion: HD, PD, home; transplant. - Conservative care if frail/poor prognosis. - Patient education programs.

