(6) GI: PPI for reflux; prokinetic (metoclopramide, erythromycin); SIBO antibiotic rotation; nutrition;

(7) Avoid high-dose steroid (SRC precipitator);

(8) Cardiac: HF, arrhythmia, pericardial effusion — monitor + treat
