(1) Echinocandin first-line: caspofungin 70 mg LD then 50 mg/d, micafungin 100 mg/d, anidulafungin 200 mg LD then 100 mg/d — broad-spectrum + fungicidal + good safety + cover non-albicans + activity vs biofilm;

